msgid ""
"If you are outside the US, we recommend NOWPayments (lowest fees, direct to "
"your wallet). If you are in the US, Stripe Crypto is also an option. You can"
" enable multiple services and let your visitors choose!"
msgstr ""
"Um tú ert utan US, eru okkum til hvat NOWPayments (lítst loyn, beint til "
"tína lóg). Um tú ert innan US, er Stripe Crypto eisini ein val. Tú mást "
"gilda fleiri þjónustur og lata dine viðvísandi velja!"

