msgid ""
"Stripe Crypto payments (USDC) are ONLY available for US-based businesses. If"
" you are outside the US, Stripe will only accept credit card payments to "
"your Stripe balance (not directly to crypto)."
msgstr ""
"Stripe Crypto greiðslur (USDC) eru eingin einungis til yfirmaður frá US. Um "
"tú ert utan US, vil Stripe eingin greiðsluakningar við kreditkort til tín "
"Stripe saldo (ikkje direkte til kripto)."

msgid ""
"If you are in the US, you can use Stripe to receive crypto directly. If "
"outside, consider NOWPayments or CoinGate for direct crypto payouts."
msgstr ""
"Um tú ert í US, kan tú brúka Stripe til at mótga kripto direkte. Um tú ert "
"utan, vurdur NOWPayments ella CoinGate til direkte kripto utbetalningar."

