msgid "Let My Girl Friend Enjoy Our Coffee"
msgstr "Lat min kvinnulíka njóta okkara kaff"

msgid ""
"A powerful, free donation and payment widget that allows your visitors to "
"support you via credit card or cryptocurrency (Quai). No monthly fees, no "
"third-party subscriptions – just your wallet and free services."
msgstr ""
"Ein kraftfullur, gratis donations- og greiðslutólur, sum lar tínir besøkandi"
" stuttastur við kreditkort ella krypto (Quai). Ongar månadslegar gjaldar, "
"inga tredjepartsabonnement – einans tín vesle og gratis túnaðir."

msgid ""
"Some browsers block third-party scripts for privacy. This proxy loads "
"scripts through your own server to bypass these blocks."
msgstr ""
"Nokkurir vafragir blokkar tredjeparts skriptir fyri personliga varðveiting. "
"Hetta proxy hleður skriptir gjøgnum tínar egna servery til at skipa hesi "
"blokker."

msgid ""
"You can update the script URLs below if the original URLs change or if you "
"want to use a different CDN."
msgstr ""
"Tú kanst uppdatera skript URLir niðanfyri, um upprunaligar URLir skiftar "
"ella um tú vil brúka ein annan CDN."

